column1: 1) extract rar file to desired directory
2) go to dircetory and open the setting.config file, scroll down to bottom where it says
be sure to change this to the appropriate web browser you are using.
3) then pin the Zbot application to the ask bar.
4) start the app, it will open the web brouser and attempt to go to Zyanga via facebook. log in and go to Zyanga poker.
5) you are now in the Zyanga lobby, the Zbot chat window win say to go to a empty 9 seat table. do so, it will take a moment to sit at each seat. let the bot finish recording the seat positions.
(if it does get interupted press esc and find another empty room and start the app again).
6) once completed it will take you back to the lobby, then find a room and walllaahhh your done.

if it ever says in the chat window, bad rooom or blinds too high. these conditions can be changed in the settings.config file. after a while you will get to learn how the scoring works and there is a small hellp file in the rar. when making changes to the config file, take care and only making small adjustments.
